channel.title: HELP! Putting my server online
channel.description: Well the title says it all, but heres the problem. Yes, i have had a server before, so I know how to do it. But I create the server, have a no-ip, but my server isnt recongnizing the no-ip, or at least reacting to it. I have both running, but i cant use the no-ip to put it online. What am I doing wrong? :confused:
